{"tid":1287303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生於紅底屋企真係好無奈","createTime":"2019-07-05T06:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:34:22.000Z","uid":68688,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4aa378bfb1c9d29d45f2f36dd88510ca1471931","tid":1287303,"uid":68688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"屋企人都係紅底 <br />\n只用微信溝通 到宜家我大個仲搬埋上大陸<br />\n<br />\n佢把我生於香港讓成為香港人<br />\n但就唔接受我愛香港 唔比我發夢<br />\n佢知道左個夢之後不但沒支持仲搵成班紅底親戚一齊話我<br />\n每一日雞同鴨講 每一日都要受佢地冷言<br />\n佢地永遠唔會明我地個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實真係好無奈<br />\n<br />\n好羨慕人地一家人一齊發同一個夢<br />\n每次見到死士出現個人就愈黎愈負面<br />\n男朋友港豬 身邊朋友都係港豬<br />\n搞到好似無人支持無人明白自己咁<br />\n但我知道 大家都攰 但都會撐落去 所以我都會堅持繼續發夢！<br />\n<br />\n我唔知自己打呢段說話有咩用<br />\n就當我鼓勵下自己或者鼓勵下身同感受既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無嘢講啦 加油！一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nGFZ6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nGFZ6K.png&h=93a05d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpDMML.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpDMML.png&h=7d89cda5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8vLrMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8vLrMN.png&h=880b3b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aca8d5cb99b4cab5c4b95dd7b61abfe41855373","tid":1287303,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"幫手俾意見<br />\n<br />\n一人一信  no DQ  還我選舉權  <br />\n唔好比藉口人地將好的議員篩走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=35588aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV</a>"},{"pid":"8d164c9d490caeb3648cea20e846073a6f03b09c","tid":1287303,"uid":191701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"如果係有錢既紅底家庭仲可以飲飲食食 當無事發生tim"},{"pid":"e5c25caae07959d7a8438767f8587247f55c2891","tid":1287303,"uid":260312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"好過有啲連登仔口講反共 轉頭就入去淘寶post 到討論<br />\n仲要討論咗四十幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1c5d0d5ca58cbb35e88265f299246639ef1189","tid":1287303,"uid":68688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c25caae07959d7a8438767f8587247f55c2891","tid":1287303,"uid":260312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"好過有啲連登仔口講反共 轉頭就入去淘寶post 到討論<br />\n仲要討論咗四十幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"討論內容咩先"},{"pid":"b2b773a758f75b75f255d236a5b7216443032a32","tid":1287303,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我好你少少自己一個住<br />\n平時出街食飯都可以各持己見蜻蜓點水<br />\n如果同屋企人住我真係唔知頂到佢地洗腦幾耐"},{"pid":"06187e5177d8c51768d720bee8c7efce218534d5","tid":1287303,"uid":68688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b773a758f75b75f255d236a5b7216443032a32","tid":1287303,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我好你少少自己一個住<br />\n平時出街食飯都可以各持己見蜻蜓點水<br />\n如果同屋企人住我真係唔知頂到佢地洗腦幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"同男朋友住 但男朋友係港豬<br />\n不但不支持仲比佢話我擊進分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以先話